      { q: "What is the best outfit for brunch?", a: "For brunch, smart-casual is the sweet spot. For women, a wrap dress, a linen set, or tailored wide-leg trousers with a silk blouse work beautifully. For men, chinos, a well-fitted shirt, and clean loafers or white trainers are a reliable choice." },
      { q: "Is there a dress code for brunch?", a: "Most brunches don't have a strict dress code — smart-casual is the safe standard. Avoid overly formal attire and overly casual looks like gym wear or flip-flops unless the venue specifically invites it." },
